<i>adverb</i>: 홀가분히 [홀가분히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>홀가분히 [홀가분히]</dt><br>
<dd>lightheartedly; carefreely</dd><br>
<dd>신경이 쓰이거나 귀찮지 않고 가볍고 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of feeling light and comfortable without being burdened or bothered by something.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>